review_text:
Was playing Advanced diff as FNaF characters made it to the second to last level with with 1 hp left and bot teamates have BARLEY any HP themselves, then as we are like a room or two from the safe room finally after an hour or 2 worth of attempts just for a charger to spawn right around the corner and then proceeds  to charge me off the building ending that run.

15/10 will always play again, especily because It took me way too long to make a review when I litteraly love the game and have for years but again I love played it for a few months before I couldnt play it on xbox and finally recently like last year bought the game and joyfully played it again. 

Valve please make a Left 4 Dead 3, we dont need a full brand new game but huge bonus if so just go full in with mod support making customs maps and stuff WITHIN the game like a game creator but ony Left 4 Dead stuff. :P pls ;-;
